channel.title: Foundation Industries?
channel.description:
Hello.
I haven't played Satisfactory about a year. I came back after watched Update 5 (I know coming soon) and played a little bit. One thing I really like mod called Foundation Industries which I used alot in the past - and I just noticed the mod is "out of date".
I'm wondering if it still works even with red triangle "out of date"?
